content: I'll definitely check out those online stores. I'm actually a fan of ASOS, I've ordered from them before and their shipping is really fast. Speaking of which, I got a bunch of new dresses and tops from them about two weeks ago, including a really cute flowy maxi dress that I wore to brunch last weekend. Anyway, back to the graphic tee... do you think a bright yellow or coral graphic tee would look better with the distressed denim jeans and gold necklace?
